Workgroups a window-configuration persistence package.

== Features ==

* Storage and restoration of window configs
* Saving and loading of window configs
* Base and working configs for each workgroup
* Killing and yanking of window configs
* Animated window config morphing
* Lots of other stuff

== Get Workgroups ==

Here: http://github.com/tlh/workgroups.el


